{"tid":1200493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想寫隻game係專救人，有冇人有興趣","createTime":"2019-06-10T18:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T07:56:22.000Z","uid":17070,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2b047c8a4887fad35ece38aed7a7ff5695942ea4","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"主要玩法係當一位隊友比敵人制服既時候<br />\n其他玩家就組成一隊小隊衝去救佢<br />\n<br />\n職業選擇有<br />\n1.前排<br />\n兩手空空，無任何裝備，主要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">拉番起被制服既隊友</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.中排<br />\n手持<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">噴漆</span></span>，射向敵人眼/頭盔/眼罩，奪取敵方視野<br />\n<br />\n3.後排<br />\n手持<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">油/波子/煙霧彈</span></span>準備，以防敵方增援<br />\n<br />\n目標主要救人為主，唔好浪費時間打/圍毆敵人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以速度為第一考慮因素</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n之前玩過d game好多時只可以眼甘甘成班人睇住自己友比人制服，剩係可以靠把口嘴遁，而呢個玩法就睇大家會唔會將佢成為主流<br />\n<br />\n目前諗到咁多，有冇巴絲有興趣一齊寫game/會想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777c1002bd71cee6509acf492a0e47c1f8882f04","tid":1200493,"uid":95624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41e01ec879f974f4e48c4ee2b6dde14c7a095442","tid":1200493,"uid":41292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:25:25.000Z","msg":"想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9542331d34ec4586254b0dd8b3055b04266055","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yx1Grbz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYx1Grbz.png&h=8ccf202a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24bff59c98833f0fa725440946f1555004a5a8c6","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:26:21.000Z","msg":"自由組隊,噴漆為最重要物資"},{"pid":"00efc8408b48f12bcaed89b6a78c5f48ef619cda","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5391852fa07dde9b22a1995759e1959a19a50e36","tid":1200493,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:35:25.000Z","msg":"對game design有興趣 推"},{"pid":"d154522061f776e8ce8a3ea578539787b15da402","tid":1200493,"uid":67069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:36:20.000Z","msg":"隻game好似幾好玩"},{"pid":"daa7e31381c936f27b7b215d089b5dad72383cb3","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"仲有第4個職業，就係物資部<br />\n買多d噴漆派比人，教埋人地隻game個玩法"},{"pid":"b0dcb32cd82b02cd916b232cac1925dc80f6f330","tid":1200493,"uid":220479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:41:03.000Z","msg":"G持 <br />\n犧牲一個就少一個<br />\n好鐘意玩呢類合作嘅game"},{"pid":"3cb44758fdf7e3c9527fb7667232eb2051916ed2","tid":1200493,"uid":144435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"daa7e31381c936f27b7b215d089b5dad72383cb3","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"仲有第4個職業，就係物資部<br />\n買多d噴漆派比人，教埋人地隻game個玩法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:43:47.000Z","msg":"物資部仲可以準備定多啲油<br />\n最好有埋醫療隊 負責傷口處理"},{"pid":"f8d0a823a11185c92148f796207f528710764136","tid":1200493,"uid":162057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:44:11.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"7d51575d94fe2ba414b43f12a4522d1fc084cec0","tid":1200493,"uid":198223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:46:16.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"01245db1ec1f18d9773cf0a552c4b599923e4d11","tid":1200493,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:46:46.000Z","msg":"個人覺得 感覺可以似the escapist<br />\n自己得好小物資，用策略贏班狗"},{"pid":"3bcf2f6da77c8bd10e003700e1493a51b8e5038c","tid":1200493,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07fd9f79afa404f2373461cd6e7488dbf23e12f","tid":1200493,"uid":155493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:47:17.000Z","msg":"要整D指令 去指揮大家點行 唔係正常大家唔太可能心連心估到幾時再一齊衝"},{"pid":"a4d4f71cb51d0a8a2adffe04e99251cb4de5d2ac","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c24975d34018cf99760b20f87818301ad4ca21","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b23b8066b47f05f97cbfc47ed593838260074b","tid":1200493,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T20:00:34.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"55f277a736c96928e3e9d65077ea98cd32d2e2cf","tid":1200493,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T20:06:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"857a2358e2f543d8485ed7cbbe3c3ca42b809587","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeee92bf37ddd4055717ac95ae234628883858bb","tid":1200493,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:31:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63b30071379261c66e46080052e1682d00fe2f39","tid":1200493,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"唔好再眼甘甘望住自己友比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8a7b6c42ab4aef43e3cd5df42b5abb70f1e68c","tid":1200493,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"TG 見到有人po <br />\n<br />\n根據大家討論內容 嘗試整合一下：<br />\n<br />\n❌注意：一啲會Team Kill(TK)嘅嘢唔好用啦：屎，粉塵塵爆❌<br />\n<br />\n✅火攻：後期需要行動「再升級」先用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家可能會有其他戰術<br />\n又會有鬼睇穿哂 <br />\n唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n*只少袋住一個戰術方案先，亂起上嚟六神無主起碼記得仲有一個戰術跟得到*<br />\n<br />\n先後流程：<br />\n<br />\n1）砲撃，水彈/硬物/其他投擲物，要掉嘅掉唒先(之後大家追逐戰好難分心到去掉野)<br />\n<br />\n2)各自行動，要用噴漆槍嘅就噴，要用棍扑人就扑，要用強光嘅就照，行動時唔好怕柒，好似玩糖黐豆咁 五六個人一小隊，自動自覺組隊啦，未有隊嘅就問身邊人：「一齊組隊ok？」，比速龍暴龍包嘅人 <br />\n<br />\n小隊記得救返隊友 <br />\n小隊記得救返隊友 <br />\n小隊記得救返隊友<br />\n<br />\n好重要所以講三次<br />\n<br />\n(完)"}]}